sentences: Jess Lee Kar Wei (Chinese: 李佳薇; pinyin: Lǐ Jiāwēi, born June 1, 1988 in Seremban, Negeri Sembilan, Malaysia), is a finalist and grand winner of the popular televised singing competition One Million Star (7th Season) in Taiwan.
She currently resides in Taiwan and has attended the National Taiwan University as an exchange student.
In September 2011, Lee's first album, Thank You My Love (感謝愛人), was debuted under the label Warner Music Taiwan.
